rows.label: tlk43600143_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Don't you think that goods have gotten
a lot cheaper in Fons Maim lately?

rows.label: tlk43600143_03_msg0002
rows.name: I for one am glad for that!

rows.label: tlk43600143_03_msg0003
rows.name:
What? There's a movement to
increase foreign trade and get more
products on the market?

rows.label: tlk43600143_03_msg0004
rows.name:
My son told me trade would improve
as the mercenaries in Gar-something
or other completed missions.
